- Update AUTHORS file
- git flow release start {release}
- Update version number in __init__.py
- Update version number in latest "Upgrading" section in docs
- git flow release finish {release}
- git checkout {release}
- ./setup.py sdist upload
- scp sdist file to my own server
- Run ``fab publish_docs`` to publish release documentation.
- git checkout master
- Increase version number, append 'dev'